a:5:{s:5:"title";s:89:"OpenCRM applies Opportunity Probability and Weighted Amount across Revenue Forecast rows";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:904:"<p>OpenCRM shipped an update to the Revenue Forecast section in Opportunities that applies the parent Opportunity’s Probability and Weighted Amount to every Revenue Forecast line item.</p>
<h3>Context</h3>
<p>Revenue Forecast lets teams split an Opportunity’s value across expected revenue periods (for example, partial billing at project start and the remainder at completion).</p>
<h3>What changed</h3>
<p>Previously, Revenue Forecast rows didn’t automatically align with the parent Opportunity’s probability/weighting. With this update, OpenCRM allows the Opportunity’s Probability and Weighted Amount to be applied across all forecast rows, keeping the forecast breakdown consistent with the Opportunity’s weighted revenue view.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://productupdates.opencrm.co.uk/en/news/393">https://productupdates.opencrm.co.uk/en/news/393</a></p>
";s:9:"text-flow";a:6:{i:0;s:183:"OpenCRM shipped an update to the Revenue Forecast section in Opportunities that applies the parent Opportunity’s Probability and Weighted Amount to every Revenue Forecast line item.";i:1;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:7:"Context";}i:2;s:171:"Revenue Forecast lets teams split an Opportunity’s value across expected revenue periods (for example, partial billing at project start and the remainder at completion).";i:3;a:2:{i:0;s:2:"h2";i:1;s:12:"What changed";}i:4;s:332:"Previously, Revenue Forecast rows didn’t automatically align with the parent Opportunity’s probability/weighting. With this update, OpenCRM allows the Opportunity’s Probability and Weighted Amount to be applied across all forecast rows, keeping the forecast breakdown consistent with the Opportunity’s weighted revenue view.";i:5;s:65:"Learn more here: https://productupdates.opencrm.co.uk/en/news/393";}s:4:"meta";a:2:{s:14:"links-required";a:0:{}s:18:"resources-detected";a:0:{}}}s:7:"summary";s:224:"OpenCRM shipped an update to the Revenue Forecast section in Opportunities that applies the parent Opportunity’s Probability and Weighted Amount to every Revenue Forecast line item. | Read fresh CRM news at WeekCRM";s:14:"comments-count";i:0;s:9:"tags-data";a:2:{s:5:"ctree";a:3:{i:0;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:3:"CRM";s:4:"href";s:34:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/crm/";}i:1;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:7:"opencrm";s:4:"href";s:38:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/opencrm/";}i:2;a:3:{s:8:"visible?";b:1;s:4:"name";s:15:"product updates";s:4:"href";s:46:"https://weekcrm.com/blog/tags/product-updates/";}}s:20:"all-resnames-uploads";a:0:{}}}